<strong>Role Summary</strong></p>
<p>
Our product design is driven by efficacy research in second language acquisition, but we are truly differentiated in the language market by our cutting edge technology platform, serving web and native Android and iOS clients.&nbsp; We are building a scalable service oriented platform around patented algorithms, not a cardboard box around a CD-ROM, so our tech-driven startup culture is unique in the language education market.&nbsp; Members of the backend team solve hard problems using a bewildering array of open source software, here&rsquo;s what we&rsquo;ve been using in the last 6 months: mongodb, postgresql, redis, rabbitmq, beanstalkd, elastic search, hadoop+pig+EMR, numpy/scipy/scikit-learn, NLTK, memcached, varnish, nginx, uwsgi, python, gevent, bottle.py, django, fabric, chef, jenkins+nose and naturally it&rsquo;s all checked into git.</p>
