<strong>Role Description</strong></p>
<p>
Voxy is looking for a talented front-end engineer who wants to dramatically improve the way millions of people around the world learn English. We have a cutting-edge frontend stack at Voxy: we use Backbone, Backbone.Marionette and RequireJS to present a seamless interface to a Django app on the backend. It&rsquo;s okay if you haven&rsquo;t worked with these particular tools, but we expect that you can pick them up quickly (or even make informed, calculated recommendations for alternatives).</p>
<p>
We write JavaScript, CoffeeScript and Python, so you should be extremely familiar with JavaScript (syntax, scoping rules; bonus points for ES5 knowledge) and comfortable in at least one common &ldquo;server-side&rdquo; language, as you&rsquo;ll be working in both the browser and on the server (we run Ubuntu). You&rsquo;ll need to be proficient with HTML5 and CSS3. We need to deliver our app to users promptly, so you should have knowledge of modern web performance analysis and optimization techniques as well.</p>
<p>
Our development environment is fast-paced and Agile, so you should be too. Have a GitHub account or a blog? Let us know!</p>
<p>
All of these tools that you either know or are eager to learn enable us to build revolutionary language learning applications that are exciting, engaging and effective. Come work with Voxy to build a cutting-edge web app that will help improve the lives and careers of millions of people.</p>
<p>
<strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Outstanding engineering talent as shown through past projects and positions, either independent or professional</li>
<li>
3 or more years experience working with web technologies</li>
<li>
Demonstrable experience with modern web application technologies (HTML5, CSS3, modern web frameworks, etc.)</li>
<li>
Solid understanding of CS fundamentals either via an educational background in Computer Science or devoted personal learning</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Working here, you&#39;ll enjoy:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Competitive salary and stock options</li>
<li>
Medical, Dental, Vision, Flex Spending benefits</li>
<li>
Sweet office space in downtown Manhattan, with an awesome team of super creative, talented, and motivated individuals</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>About us:</strong><br />
Voxy is a NYC-based company that is using mobile/web applications and sophisticated personalization technology to disrupt the $80B market for language education. Since launch in 2010 as a TechCrunch Disrupt finalist, Voxy has grown to over 2.5M users, tens of thousands of paying customers, and has the #1 rated education app in Brazil, Mexico, and dozens of other countries around the world. Voxy is backed by leading education investors, and has been recognized as a pioneer by The New York Times, CNN Money, Fast Company, Mashable, Univision, Veja (Brazil), Venturebeat, and others.</p>
